value: Resident, grassland and open savanna: C Namibia, Botswana, South Africa away from coastal areas and much of E side.

flat gassland with grass 50-100cm high, open shrub veld, semi-desert scrub, grassy dunes and dry bush savanna, often in heavily grazed areas or those with patchy, sparse grass cover including old cropland
